#31517
the Pine Forest~
   Deep in the forest you have exits in all four cardinal directions.  West
will take you further from the road.  East will do the opposite.  North,
forest, and south...  More forest.  Looking up your view of the sky is limited
by the tree limbs and vegetation.  The ground is moist, thick with pine straw
and moss.  
