#31599
A Massive Grave~
   Seems you found yourself in a pickle.  A pretty rank and unsanitary pickle
jar would be more like it.  There are bodies of several races and species here
in every stage of decomposition.  The walls of this pit are muddy and angled
in such a manner that climbing out is impossible.  Why did you come down here?
Didn't you look before you went?  Calling out for help is impossible, the soft
ground, rotting flesh, and moss seem to absorb any sound from escaping.  Your
move..  
~
